# mydiary

MyDiary is an online journal that provides users with the ability to pen down their thoughts and feelings

## User Registration [/api/v1/auth/signup]

### Register a new user [POST]

A user can be signed up using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a username, email, password, and password confrimation

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "david",
            "email": "dave@gmail.com",
            "password": "1234",
            "confirm_password": "1234"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/auth/signup

